Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:47.29,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 14 - A Stout Man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Marsh,\Naren't baby goats cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:39.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Marsh. I got to keep a handful of animals again,\Njust like back in England!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Marsh!\NBaby goat may step on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! It's so awfully early,\Nbut you're already up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause I can't ever get any sleep\Nin a place so cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:22.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, it's where we two\Nwill always have to sleep, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too cramped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well isn't it why dad promised\Nto rebuild it bigger with time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't do that on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course it won't happen tomorrow\Nor the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:33.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sleep in a tent.\NI feel better in spacious places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that might be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Deighton and Ben\Nalso need some place to sleep at now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And those two are still just sleeping peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because our brother and Mr. Deighton, the doctor,\Nsuddenly needed a place to sleep at,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:50.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,me and Lucy-May\Nhad to relinquish our tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Baby goats look healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Marsh! You're still there?\NCome here now, boy. It's dangerous there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Marsh is acting big.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Marsh wants to examine\Nthe baby goats from all possible sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Marsh? Are you alright, Marsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:47.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he feels mighty embarrassed\Nfor being squashed by a baby goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The weather looks perfect today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:05:00.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the sea was calm last night,\Nso I slept well without any rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you've disembarked the ship already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:12.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!\NI have come to live in Adelaide now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. And you spent a night in our tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go see the neighbor\Nwho's been ill now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be serious if the fever didn't subside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah...\NSo I really hope it did subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, sorry to trouble you,\Nbut can't you go fetch some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, brother!\NI'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two should go gather some firewood instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's any\Nfallen firewood near the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not awfully attentive, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.\NWe'll go there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there is some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to visit the Macs again, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Aye... Thought I should check\Non the patient's condition. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bero-bero-bero-baa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hoity-toity-oity-baa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could someone please bring Tob outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tob...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me\Nto help with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not for the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:39.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you if there's something\NI absolutely can't do without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, feel free to call me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Without any profound repairs done,\Nthere is still barely any smoke outflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Lucy-May!\NC'mere for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a strange animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, it got four limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I saw it in the water over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come slowly to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's there! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It got a beak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a waterfowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've not seen a bird\Nwith four feet ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:17.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It got a tail, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It went over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A strange thing, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Australia has some of the most\Npeculiar animals, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you're not thinking of keeping\Nthis animal as a pet, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it, if it ever returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dig a pond in front of our house\Nfor keeping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:51.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, make sure\Nyou don't fall into the river again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Last time you nearly drowned, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was because I was trying to save Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Also, hurry up with gathering the firewood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:14.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, we didn't get to see\Nthat bizarre animal there ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:21.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until a much much later point that we learned this animal was actually called platypus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think we could capture it alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy-May,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:30.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little curious, do you plan to keep\Nthings like snakes and lizards, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you can't be serious when saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even those disgusting snakes and lizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna build a whole zoo of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:45.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the snakes and lizards. That animal from before is about as much as I can tolerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you look closely,\Nsnakes and lizards are cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:52.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear what dad said?\NAround here, some snakes and lizards are poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But such things are not common.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just forget about snakes and lizards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:00.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you so insist, I will give\Nsnakes and lizards the least priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Only when I would have collected all the other animals,\NI'll go after snakes and lizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You got problems to solve\Neven so early in the morning, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem is the patient.\NThe fever still won't subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That is distressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:36.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm done eating my breakfast,\NI'll go to the city center to look for the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think they have any medicine there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,According to Bernard, they have\Nall kinds of medications at the governor's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for emergency situations and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:50.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since we can't get them in a proper store, I guess we've no choice but to ask the governor to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:54.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, while we're at it,\Nwhat exactly is Mr. Mac's illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. That's something I don't know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:02.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have contracted it after going\Ndeep into the hinterland for the surveying work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:07.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning he may have been stung there by some insect,\Ncarrying a pathogen that we don't know a thing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of disease\Nis problematic, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good job.\NJust leave it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Coming later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When going out to the wilderness,\Nyou two ought to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:30.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Around here, you might find yourself\Nin great peril any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At such times, your only option to make it through\Nmay be through sticking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes I absolutely can't stand\Nsticking with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, no... Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, why don't you\Nhave breakfast inside, with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I was just getting real hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:35.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you actually plan to do\Nfrom now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, you slept here,\Nbut what about tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:42.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Guess I'm homeless now, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:46.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that would suit you,\Nyou're welcome to stay here for some while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:51.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's what I'll do. I can't think\Nof a single other place I could stay at...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only it's not too big an inconvenience to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's no inconvenience at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:59.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, I feel ashamed somehow\Nfor making you sleep in a shabby tent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Life in a tent ain't half bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you recognize him? Remember,\Nthe man that saved me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:30.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can put that firewood down right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:34.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, we gotta pay our gratitude somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, anything would do, I reckon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, breakfast is going cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, this is the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The one who saved Lucy-May\Nthe day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so I wanted to thank him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I think it's a good idea, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But what is it we could present him with\Nto make him really happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Some edible might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... What about clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be something to drink, if ya ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Ain't that right, mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something to drink?\NLike what, for instance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let's say, could be whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then beer, maybe wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And we've neither again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning you've not a bit of alcohol here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,None, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How about some of yesterday's bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it should totally do.\NThat one was very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, then I'll go get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This here is my entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:01.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom will now bring the bread\Nthat we wanted to present you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the bread that I baked.\NPlease try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy stuff!\NCome on, taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um, mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Smells just as good, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How are you finding my bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:40.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say we made him mighty happy with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His people don't know\Nhow to bake bread, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:01.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They grew up in the wild,\Nwhere they've only ever eaten plants and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they drink alcohol, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt they can brew it all on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? So not drinking alcohol either?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, some odd fellas they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There we go! Right! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:20.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The man who owned this prefabricated home before\Nsaid he could try to assemble it in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks? Impossible! It's three weeks,\Neven if we rush it to the utmost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of living in a tent so much\Nthat I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And my wife feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I want that house built, and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:42.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! And... there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... There it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now move it, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen that man's face somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Pettywell, who came on the same ship as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh-oh! It's {\i1}that{\i0} man, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know, he's quite a taskmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a consequence of being dirty rich, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:03.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. So that's what money does to people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the economy here is booming,\Nso the houses would soon mushroom anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it considered polite\Nnot to say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That house used to be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? And what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:22.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That prefabricated home\Nwas the house that {\i1}we{\i0} brought along from England!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Petty complains won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Doctor finds the medicine he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:43.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you think they have their own cart at the sawmill,\Nfor moving the lumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They gotta have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Without it, their clients won't be able to transport\Nthe timber they bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Further ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be an oxcart they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?\NI need you back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My... Where could they have gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:15.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange. I definitely heard those two\Ntalking here a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:25.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to make a little trip\Nto the Adelaide city center.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we start here, we're immediately on the road,\Nso there's no way we get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there aren't many buildings yet,\Nso you can see us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't even go all that terribly far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll only take a stroll to Colonel Light's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we look at Mr. Bernard's working place,\Nwe'll turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:45.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There is something else\NI need you two to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, just some simple job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something even Lucy-May can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:51.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I was hoping Kate would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go play around some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:57.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The oil is viscous enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can stop stirring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:13.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I was already feeling stiff in the chest.\NIt smells so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not something we can help, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's just some oil leftovers\Nthat we scrambled together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:26.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no longer anything for me to do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! You now need to watch closely\Nto what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, you'll also be doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This place is no England for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something we can do ourselves,\Nwe do it ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But there's plenty of candles for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But those are expensive.\NNow watch how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We do it like this, making sure the yarn\Nis thoroughly soaked in oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About this should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now we leave it to dry up in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's be one mighty long and narrow candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, we'll yet have to repeat\Nthis process many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:05.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once it congeals, we dip it in oil,\Nthen drying it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once it congeals, dip in oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:08.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it gradually thickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Takes quite a while to finish, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:16.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Might take several days, or even weeks\Nuntil it finally starts to resemble a candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I got some oil on my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:31.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can wash it away later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Now I got the oil on my clothes, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:50.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's done,\Nwe'll have to pull the cart by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't got much choice.\NNo oxen or horses around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:56.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way we carry it all in one run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:58.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll manage if you hire someone extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've got the cart already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We'll try to get it done by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever suits you, mate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:18.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, this kind of job\Nrequires a great deal of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:46.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'm glad they let you have\Nthe medicine needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:50.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye. The office folk were mighty understanding\Ntowards our unforeseen plight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They agreed to divert some medicine\Nfrom their own stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:56.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, you could run\Na private practice in that tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:01.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone in our neighbors' house\Nis well and healthy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:03.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I expect the fever to subside come morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is taking dad and Ben\Nridiculously long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, let's rest a tad bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:00.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:07.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mr. Popple, s'that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:10.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Popple here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:13.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Your dad and brother are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:15.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:30.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:33.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Ben, let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:37.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:39.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:41.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:47.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and Ben brought along\Na whole lot of lumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:50.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we can finally start expanding the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:55.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And when we do, our sleep will be\Nway more sound than now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:07.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've never seen our neighbor Mr. Mac,\Nso we were starting to wonder if he's even real.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:11.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just can't take it anymore!\NWe'll have to peek inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:15.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Two Homes".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.28,0:24:16.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
